<emphasis id="6ECFA210FFFFFF9DFADBFEEFFACA4461" bold="true" box="[1365,1379,338,364]" pageId="3" pageNumber="188">–</emphasis>
19.5 × 7.9 
<emphasis id="6ECFA210FFFFFF9DFF25FECBFF10449D" bold="true" box="[171,185,374,400]" pageId="3" pageNumber="188">–</emphasis>
